<br>
The rod in Lower Guk is a pain.  Go to Halas and purchas the ingredients for ITU potions (it will cost you like 15pp per potion instead of the 25pp going rate) and find a shaman to combine them for you.<br>
<br>
Then go to Lower Guk and wait for the Lord group to pull the hand...it may take hours, days, weeks, who knows.  Took me 3 weeks the first time of off and on poping into Guk to check on it.<br>
<br>
After that the rest is a piece of cake... <p><P></P>
